description:
Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj is a name that commands respect like no one else in Maharashtra & beyond. Yet absolute silence from some quarters after the shocking collapse of Shivaji Maharajs statue (that was inaugurated by Modi just last year)
Like promises of #AccheDin  the statue was hollow and supported by rusting iron beams. 
But Marathi Asmita does not get disrespected after this open insult to one of Indias tallest leaders? Will the Marathi Manoos not speak up because its not politically convenient to do so? 
Social Media warriors also have gone underground.
